Package net.sawannaniz.databaseclient.ctrl

This package provides a set of classes representing all entities that the database Przychodnia contains. With net.sawannaniz.databaseclient.dbutils package it provides a complete interface to Przychodnia database. It includes one interface that should be implemented by any class that wants to save data to Przychodnia database. It also includes an abstract class Searching that should be derived by any class that wants to search data in the Przychodnia database.
Since:
2023-04-09
Version:
1.0
Author:
Mateusz Marzec
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SaveableToPrzychodnia
    The interface that should be implemented by any object that is going to be saved in the Przychodnia database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Lekarz
    It represents a physician corresponding to the one stored in the table Lekarze of the database.
    Pacjent
    Represents a patient - an entity stored in the Przychodnia database.
    Pomieszczenie
    Represents a room where an appointment takes place, references this entity stored in Przychodnia database.
    Searching
    A class which should be inherited by any object that is going to be searched for in the Przychodnia database.
    Wizyta
    A class that represents an appointment in a clinic, as stored in the Przychodnia database.
